{"tid":2274520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳海面發現浮屍","createTime":"2020-11-06T13:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:31:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1366a7427e6d2c0df59330627a57cb65be6778","tid":2274520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/STfHjLsLSu0OspCohE90fD_nrTg=/802x379/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PKZJJLKHQFCG3DBUTA4KU4CTCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSTfHjLsLSu0OspCohE90fD_nrTg%3D%2F802x379%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPKZJJLKHQFCG3DBUTA4KU4CTCM.jpg&h=d51405a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午5時許，有市民赫見一具人形物體，在將軍澳日出康城對出海面載浮載沉，於是報警。水警到場證實是一具浮屍，將其撈起並在附近唐俊街的海濱公園碼頭上岸。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，死者為一名上年紀男子，身上並無身份證明文件。警方一度向附近釣魚人士及公園的街坊查問，但暫時未有目擊者看到有人墮海，正調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201106/6MOWWWYN4ZADBIO2G5U2JGZIOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201106%2F6MOWWWYN4ZADBIO2G5U2JGZIOA%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9qCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d4b9a795\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201106%2F6MOWWWYN4ZADBIO2G5U2JGZIOA%2F&h=75342129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201106/6MOWWWYN4ZADBIO2G5U2JGZIOA/</a>"},{"pid":"35ffa22f0f0ac798156c8348591c82cbb3bdbc59","tid":2274520,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"又殺人"},{"pid":"02cecb32b17b1cb643f85c07cec600ea5df633c1","tid":2274520,"uid":356542,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92f8780370a9299fd0eb41f513bc66a85cbce97a","tid":2274520,"uid":310275,"like":